{{Top|leg}}
The '''Crimson Condottiere''' were the rarest and highest ranking of [[Xim/Legends|Xim's]] [[war-robot]]s. They employed [[Rakata/Legends|Rakatan]] Force-energizing dynamos.<ref name="TNEGtD">''[[The New Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> Covered with thick armor plating that was coated with a mirrored reflective surface for deflecting enemy fire and reinforced stress points, they were dangerous foes.

